aadi Karke Phas Gaya Yaar]]'' |1 song- "Deewane Dil Ko" |- |''Dhadkanein'' |All Songs. co-lyricist Farhad |- | rowspan=3| 2005 |[[Ek Khiladi Ek Haseena (film)|''Ek Khiladi Ek Haseena'']] |2 songs- "Sara Jahan" , "Jhum Baho Mein" |- |''Jalwa'' |All Songs. co-lyricists Arun Malik, Asad Ajmeri |- |''[[Kaal]]'' |2 songs- "Iss Kal Kal Me Ham" , "Tauba Tauba Ishq Main Kariya" |- | rowspan=2| 2004 |''Mission Mumbai'' |1 song- "Mumbai Mein Aake" |- |''[[Garv]]'' |Debut film as lyricist |- |}
